{"tid":225096,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[中學雞] 搵到暑期工仲未開始返過工就俾人炒撚左","createTime":"2017-05-01T13:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T02:59:40.000Z","uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f50fa6acdbb970fe39abc98fa6ae4bfe6df3819a","tid":225096,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"話說我見考DSE都考得七七八八就諗住搵份暑期工做,<br />\nsend左十幾封email終於有回應,其中一間叫我上個星期五去見工,<br />\n見果陣都順順利利,佢果邊係運動用品鋪頭仔黎,問我識唔識啲基本野之類咁,<br />\n如無意外就呢個星期開始返一至五做sales,果陣都覺得ok,<br />\n<br />\n跟住琴日打機打到3點先訓,今朝10點佢果邊打過黎嘈醒我訓覺,<br />\n老細:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :喂?唔係9點返工架咩?你塞車定點啊?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :下?今日要返咩......紅日喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你紅日出街係咪全世界收晒鋪無野賣架?禮拜五果陣都講到明返一至五架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我間學校今日唔洗返學喎,你係咪果啲詐騙電話黎架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我唔理你痴咩線,一個鐘內要同我返到黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我岩岩先起身姐嘛,邊有咁快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :吓?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :但我一陣約左人lunch呀,你1130放我工得唔得,我晏晝仲要陪fd玩,約好左架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :得得得,你以後都唔洗再黎<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就收左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生平最討厭呢啲僱主係到剝削員工, 而加仲要搞到我咁委屈, 好似我錯晒咁, 請問各位巴絲有無辦法告到佢破產?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8a070ceb1a888f20ea5e992ed7492849835ec4","tid":225096,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img s